snippet.title: Chester's Revenge: The Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Chester's Revenge is a story of how a carrot can corrupt even the most wonderful of guinea pigs into foul creatures. 

More about Chester coming soon! Wishlist and follow the game on Steam now to know more: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1739620/Chesters_Revenge/

Join our Discord: https://discord.bonusstage.co/
